<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (mạ lm tra ʿywn .. wlạ smʿt byh ậdẖạn
 wlạ ạ̉bdaⁿạ kẖṭr .. ʿalay̱ qlwb ạlbsẖr)2
 1- (ybdạ̉ nwrh ḍʿyf .. fy ạlqlb kạ̉nh ḍyf)2
 (nftḥ yftḥ wyḍyf)2 .. lmạ nṭyʿh ạ̹n ạ̉mr
 2- (dẖkrnạ fdẖkrnạh .. wdạwmnạ ʿ ạlṣlạẗ)2
 (wdy mnḥẗ m ạlạ̹lh)2 .. tyjy ạ̹n ạlʿạbd ṣbr
 3- (ạrtfʿy yạ ạ̉bwạb .. mạ kẖlạṣ sẖq ạlḥjạb)2
 (ndkẖl ʿly̱ ḥsạb)2 .. dm ạlfạdy ạlly gẖfr
 4- (ạlʿzẗ wạljlạl .. wạlrḥmẗ wạljmạl)2
 (fy ạlḥḍrẗ wạlwṣạl)2 .. dạqh ạlly ʿdy̱ wnẓr
 5- (ynẓr lynạ ạlḥnwn .. ysby mnạ ạlʿywn)2
 (srh ʿnd ạlly yṣwn)2 .. wnwrh lʿywn ạlshr
 6- (mạ ạ̉ḥly̱ ʿywn ạlạ̹ymạn .. sẖạyfạh bdwn ʿyạn)2
 (mạ ạlqlb lh ʿrfạn)2 .. wbṣyrẗ gẖyr ạlbṣr
 7- (wạlsạhr lh ạ̉ṣyl .. yʿly̱ nwrh bạllyl)2
 (bạlfrḥ wạlthlyl)2 .. tgẖnyh lw lyk ạftqr
 8- (ʿrf rwḥy bạlrwḥ .. tskn tfrḥ wtrwḥ)2
 (wyạk ạlkl yrwḥ)2 .. wạ̹n sẖbʿ ạlqlb ạntṣr
 9- (sẖfnạk fy mḥbyk .. wsẖfnạ byhm mạ lyk)2
 (wmʿạhm rwḥnạ lyk)2 .. lmạ ạlnwr fyhm ẓhr
 10- (ạlnwr jwh ạlktạb .. sẖạyfạh ʿyn ạlly tạb)2
 (yṣbḥ qlbh ktạb)2 .. nwrk fy sṭwrh ạtbdr
 11- (ḥrrtnạ mn ạlqyd .. nsjd lk ạ̉ʿẓm syd)2
 (wjhk nṭlb wnryd)2 .. mjdk wạnt ạlmntẓr
 12- (mạlnạsẖ hnạ fy ạlmnẓwr .. wmạlhạsẖ fynạ lmạ tdwr)2
 (bynnạ wmạ bynhạ swr)2 .. msẖ bynnạ wbyn ạlbsẖr
 13- (yạ syd ạlạ̉syạd .. yạ mṭlwb ạlʿbạd)2
 (mạlnạ rạḥẗ fy blạd)2 .. ạ̹lyk ạ̹nt ạlsfr</lyrics>
